Bongwater is a 1998 American black comedy film directed by Richard Sears and starring Luke Wilson , Alicia Witt , Amy Locane , Brittany Murphy , Jack Black , and Andy Dick .
Based on the 1995 book of the same name by Michael Hornburg , the film is set in Portland , Oregon , and follows an aspiring artist and marijuana dealer and his relationship with a tempestuous woman he meets through a client .